    "<div class=\"metadata-header\" style=\"display:none;\">informatica|GestaoProjetos|PMBOX-7-Edicao|principios</div><div class=\"canvas-box\" data-id=\"box-17799777422800.6884757224947218\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 26px; top: 55px; width: 448px; height: 40px; z-index: 3;\"><h1>Os 12 princípios do PMBOX 7</h1><p></p></div><div class=\"canvas-box\" data-id=\"box-17799777839570.35579265661159754\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 27px; top: 121px; width: 208px; height: 72px; z-index: 7;\"><h3>1. Stewardship</h3><p>Atuação responsável.</p><p>Uso ético dos recursos.</p></div><div class=\"canvas-box\" data-id=\"box-17799778329050.43770482504671393\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 27px; top: 219px; width: 208px; height: 56px; z-index: 6;\"><h3>2. Equipe</h3><p>Construir equipe eficaz.</p></div><div class=\"canvas-box\" data-id=\"box-17799778973750.7222772664421924\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 28px; top: 293px; width: 224px; height: 224px; z-index: 9;\"><h3>3. Stakeholders</h3><p>Engajar partes interessadas.</p><p>(stakeholder = interessado)</p><p>Exemplo:</p><pre><code></code></pre><pre><code>prefeito\nsecretarias\nusuários\nservidores\ncidadãos</code></pre><p></p></div><div class=\"canvas-box\" data-id=\"box-17799779172890.5670212900381687\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 278px; top: 132px; width: 224px; height: 88px; z-index: 11;\"><h3>4. Valor</h3><p>Foco em:</p><blockquote><p><strong>entrega de valor</strong></p></blockquote><p>Tema central do PMBOK 7.</p></div><div class=\"canvas-box\" data-id=\"box-17799779528030.8724364336109875\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 280px; top: 246px; width: 272px; height: 64px; z-index: 13;\"><h3>5. Pensamento sistêmico</h3><p>Entender dependências do projeto.</p></div><div class=\"canvas-box\" data-id=\"box-17799779723640.3265747178088281\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 282px; top: 329px; width: 160px; height: 48px; z-index: 15;\"><h3>6. Liderança</h3><p>Liderança efetiva.</p></div><div class=\"canvas-box\" data-id=\"box-17799780013940.8848926195036735\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 278px; top: 399px; width: 248px; height: 112px; z-index: 19;\"><h3>7. Adaptação (tailoring)</h3><p>Ajustar abordagem ao projeto.</p><p>Não existe:</p><pre><code></code></pre><pre><code>modelo único</code></pre><p></p></div><div class=\"canvas-box\" data-id=\"box-17799780321080.5908893999503289\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 582px; top: 67px; width: 184px; height: 48px; z-index: 21;\"><h3>8. Qualidade</h3><p>Qualidade embutida.</p></div><div class=\"canvas-box\" data-id=\"box-17799780576600.6814876228968788\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 578px; top: 142px; width: 192px; height: 64px; z-index: 23;\"><h3>9. Complexidade</h3><p>Gerenciar complexidade.</p></div><div class=\"canvas-box\" data-id=\"box-17799781046590.16612052843218394\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 578px; top: 240px; width: 176px; height: 48px; z-index: 29;\"><h3>10. Risco</h3><p>Gerenciar incertezas.</p></div><div class=\"canvas-box\" data-id=\"box-17799781747010.6164128054863681\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 477px; top: 322px; width: 304px; height: 64px; z-index: 32;\"><h3>11. Adaptabilidade e resiliência</h3><p>Capacidade de adaptação.</p></div><div class=\"canvas-box\" data-id=\"box-17799782242430.5056815414102664\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 534px; top: 416px; width: 240px; height: 56px; z-index: 34;\"><h3>12. Mudança</h3><p>Preparação para mudanças.</p></div>"
